Recommends: ffmpeg, mpv
Description: Digital Cinema Package (DCP) creator
 DCP Wizard creates valid Digital Cinema Packages from video sources,
 image sequences, and WAV audio, conforming to SMPTE ST 429 (Bv2.1)
 and Interop standards.
 .
 Features include JPEG 2000 encoding (GPU and CPU), AES-128 encryption,
 KDM generation, subtitle packaging, multi-channel audio, Dolby Atmos
 support, and integrated quality control via dcpdoctor.
 .
 Free and open-source alternative to easyDCP Creator+.
